'''Fingár''' was a son of [[Fingon]] in the early versions of the [[legendarium]].<ref name=Fin>{{SM|QA1}}, p. 213</ref> Nothing else is known about him.

== Etymology ==
The name ''Fingár'' is in [[Old English]], since it was translated by [[Ælfwine]], but no [[Elvish]] equivalent is given.<ref name=Fin/>

